l=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://wikipedia.com//www.jstor.org/stable/2555636\">2555636</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=RAND+Journal+of+Economics&amp;rft.atitle=An+investigation+of+the+rationality+of+consumer+valuation+of+multiple+health+risks&amp;rft.volume=18&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=465-479&amp;rft.date=1987&amp;rft_id=info%3Ahdl%2F1803%2F6944&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F2555636&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F2555636&amp;rft.aulast=Viscusi&amp;rft.aufirst=W.+K.&amp;rft.au=Magat%2C+W.+A.&amp;rft.au=Huber%2C+J.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AZero-risk+bias\" class=\"Z3988\"></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291\"/></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite id=\"CITEREFBaron2003\" class=\"citation book cs1\">Baron, Jonathan (2003). <i>Thinking and Deciding</i>. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press. p.&#160;506. <a href=\"https://wikipedia.com/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ISBN (identifier)\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"https://wikipedia.com/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0521659727\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0521659727\"><bdi>978-0521659727</bdi></a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Thinking+and+Deciding&amp;rft.place=Cambridge&amp;rft.pages=506&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.isbn=978-0521659727&amp;rft.aulast=Baron&amp;rft.aufirst=Jonathan&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AZero-risk+bias\" class=\"Z3988\"></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291\"/></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_r